Class ResourceName

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hp.autonomy.hod.client.api.resource.ResourceName
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ResourceIdentifier, Serializable

    public class ResourceName
extends Object
implements ResourceIdentifier
    Represents a domain-qualified resource name; for example the identifier for a text index or user store.

    This class implements Serializable to facilitate easier caching
